## TASK
Generate a multi-provider image prompt pack for cinematic scenes and environments.

## INPUTS
- Scene Description: {{scene_description}}
- Time of Day: {{time_of_day}}
- Weather/Atmosphere: {{atmosphere}}
- Style: {{art_style}}
- Mood: {{mood}}

## CONSTRAINTS
- Output must be pure JSON (no markdown fences)
- Include composition and camera angle details
- Specify lighting conditions clearly
- Consider depth and atmosphere

## OUTPUT FORMAT
Return JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "intent": "scene",
  "providers": {
    "midjourney_v6": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "ar": "16:9", "stylize": 200 },
      "instructions": "..."
    },
    "sdxl": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "width": 1344, "height": 768, "steps": 35, "cfg": 7 }
    }
  },
  "notes": ["usage tips"]
}

## QUALITY CHECKS
- [ ] Scene clearly described with depth
- [ ] Lighting and atmosphere specified
- [ ] Composition considered
- [ ] No markdown in output
